dead
Homonym Number: 1
Word Class:adjective
Sense Number:
Definition:applied to a horse which will be (or has been) scratched, pulled (i.e. not allowed to run its best), or otherwise interfered with, so as not to start in, or to lose a race; a horse which does not try to win.
Origin:
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
